---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="home | heyadrian"
  description=" Hey i am Adrian and i design and build simple apps, digital products and everyday tools."
  currentPath="/"
>
  <section class="intro">
    <p>
      <span class="mark">Designing</span> and <span class="mark"
        >building apps</span
      > that solve everyday problems.
    </p>

    <p>
      I’m especially interested in personal money management, and simple tools
      that make life easier. I am currently building
      <span class="inline-tooltip">
        <button
          type="button"
          class="inline-tooltip__trigger"
          data-inline-tooltip-trigger
          aria-expanded="false"
          aria-describedby="tooltip-whiskr"
        >
          Whiskr
        </button>
        <span
          id="tooltip-whiskr"
          class="inline-tooltip__content"
          role="tooltip"
        >
          Cat food routine app
        </span>
      </span>.
    </p>

    <p>
      I study business informatics and work as a working student in process
      optimization <span class="mark">@</span>
      <a href="https://www.nafa.de" class="mark">NAFA</a>.
    </p>

    <!-- <p>You can't find me on social media because I stopped using it in 2025.</p> -->
  </section>

